        <strong>Panelist: Choob </strong>
        <blockquote>
        <p><em>Composition and Design:</em> 2 - I like the overall design and the depth is quite nice, though maybe some foreground elements would help this more. As it is, she's quite close to the trees both in positioning and lineweight etc, so it doesn't read great at a glance. A different value on the figure or the trees, or a bolder outline around her would make things read much better and also still go with the graphic look you have going on.</p>
